org.apache.nutch.crawl

Class UrlWithScore

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.nutch.crawl.UrlWithScore
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<UrlWithScore>, Writable, WritableComparable<UrlWithScore>

    public final class UrlWithScore
extends java.lang.Object
implements WritableComparable<UrlWithScore>
    A writable comparable container for an url with score. Provides a Partitioner and RawComparator implementations for easy integration with jobs.
